#id=1
#text=Just the other day I baked a cake .
#id=2
#text=I found a recipe online for a chocolate cake that I really wanted to try , so I went to the store and bought all the ingredients .
#id=3
#text=Then I went home and put everything out onto the counter , including my mixing bowls , measuring cups , and baking dish .
#id=4
#text=The first thing I did was to mix the flour , water , sugar , butter , eggs and chocolate together in my big mixing bowl .
#id=5
#text=I then greased up my baking dish with oil , so the cake would n't stick to it while it was baking .
#id=6
#text=Then I set the oven temperature to 350 degrees and let it preheat .
#id=7
#text=After all my ingredients were in the bowl , I used a big spoon to stir everything together until it was nice and mixed up .
#id=8
#text=Then I poured the batter into my baking dish , and put it into the oven .
#id=9
#text=I let it bake for an hour , then took out the cake and let it cool .
#text=After it was cool I put icing on it , and cut it into pieces to save for later .
#text=Then I cleaned up my huge mess .
